rnal links==\n*{{hockeydb|8846}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Posavad, Mike}}\n[[Category:1964 births]]\n[[Category:Canadian ice hockey defencemen]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Peoria Rivermen (IHL) players]]\n[[Category:Peterborough Petes (ice hockey) players]]\n[[Category:Salt Lake Golden Eagles (CHL) players]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Brantford]]\n[[Category:St. Louis Blues draft picks]]\n[[Category:St. Louis Blues players]]\n\n\n{{canada-icehockey-defenceman-1960s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{BLP sources|date=May 2016}}\n{{Infobox ice hockey player\n| image =\n| image_size =\n| position = [[Defenceman|Defense]]\n| played_for = [[St. Louis Blues]]\n| shoots = Right\n| height_ft = 5\n| height_in = 11\n| weight_lb = 194\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|mf=yes|1964|1|3}}\n| birth_place = [[Brantford]], [[Ontario]], Canada\n| draft = 50th overall\n| draft_year = 1982\n| draft_team = [[St. Louis Blues]]\n| career_start = 1982\n| career_end = 1988\n}}\n'''Mike Posavad''' (born  January 3, 1964 in [[Brantford]], [[Ontario]]) is a [[Canadians|Canadian]] retired professional [[ice hockey]] player who played eight games in the [[National Hockey League]] for the [[St. Louis Blues]].\n\n==Career statistics==\n{| border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"text-align:center; width:60em\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#e0e0e0\" \n! colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" | \n! rowspan=\"99\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" | \n! colspan=\"5\" | [[Regular season]] \n! rowspan=\"99\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" | \n! colspan=\"5\" | [[Playoffs]] \n|- bgcolor=\"#e0e0e0\" \n! [[Season (sports)|Season]] \n! Team \n! League \n! GP \n! [[Goal (ice hockey)|G]] \n! [[Assist (ice hockey)|A]] \n! [[Point (ice hockey)|Pts]] \n! [[Penalty (ice hockey)|PIM]] \n! GP\n! G \n! A \n! Pts \n! PIM \n|- \n| 1979\u201380\n| Brantford Penguins\n| GHL\n| 43 || 11 || 22 || 33 || 16\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-  bgcolor=\"#f0f0f0\"\n| [[1980\u201381 OHL season|1980\u201381]]\n| [[Peterborough Petes]]